import React from 'react';
import {
  Box,
  Container,
  Typography,
  Grid,
  Card,
  CardContent,
  List,
  ListItem,
  ListItemIcon,
  ListItemText,
  Button,
} from '@mui/material';
import { styled } from '@mui/material/styles';
import {
  School,
  EmojiEvents,
  Timeline,
  GroupWork,
  Lightbulb,
  CheckCircle,
} from '@mui/icons-material';

const StyledCard = styled(Card)(({ theme }) => ({
  height: '100%',
  display: 'flex',
  flexDirection: 'column',
  transition: 'transform 0.2s',
  '&:hover': {
    transform: 'scale(1.02)',
  },
}));

const VisionMissionCard = ({ title, content, icon: Icon }) => (
  <StyledCard elevation={3}>
    <CardContent>
      <Box display="flex" alignItems="center" mb={2}>
        <Icon sx={{ fontSize: 40, color: 'primary.main', mr: 2 }} />
        <Typography variant="h5" color="primary">
          {title}
        </Typography>
      </Box>
      <Typography variant="body1">
        {content}
      </Typography>
    </CardContent>
  </StyledCard>
);

const About = () => {
  const visionMission = [
    {
      title: 'Vision',
      content: 'To be a Premier Engineering Institution focusing on Research, Innovation and Entrepreneurship.',
      icon: Lightbulb,
    },
    {
      title: 'Mission',
      content: 'To produce competent engineers with strong technical knowledge, professional ethics, and entrepreneurial skills through innovative teaching-learning processes, research, and industry collaboration.',
      icon: Timeline,
    },
  ];

  const achievements = [
    'Ranked 15th in Tamil Nadu TNEA 2024 Admissions',
    '7th Rank in Coimbatore TNEA 2024 Admissions',
    'Top 2% Scientists of the World with Sri Eshwar',
    '50+ International Partnerships',
    'NBA Accredited Programs',
    'NAAC Accredited Institution',
  ];

  const facilities = [
    'State-of-the-art Laboratories',
    'Modern Digital Library',
    'Innovation Centers',
    'Industry Collaboration Hub',
    'Sports Complex',
    'Hostel Facilities',
  ];

  return (
    <Box>
      {/* Hero Section */}
      <Box
        sx={{
          bgcolor: 'primary.main',
          color: 'white',
          py: 6,
          mb: 6,
          textAlign: 'center',
        }}
      >
        <Container>
          <Typography variant="h2" gutterBottom>
            About SECE
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="h6">
            Excellence in Engineering Education Since 2008
          </Typography>
        </Container>
      </Box>

      <Container sx={{ mb: 8 }}>
        {/* Introduction */}
        <Box sx={{ mb: 8 }}>
          <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>
            Welcome to Sri Eshwar College of Engineering
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
            Sri Eshwar College of Engineering (SECE) is a premier engineering institution located in Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu. 
            Established in 2008, SECE has consistently maintained high standards in engineering education, focusing on 
            academic excellence, research, innovation, and industry collaboration.
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
            Our institution is approved by AICTE, New Delhi, and affiliated to Anna University, Chennai. We offer various 
            undergraduate and postgraduate programs in engineering, with a strong emphasis on practical learning and 
            industry-relevant skills.
          </Typography>
        </Box>

        {/* Vision and Mission */}
        <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom textAlign="center" sx={{ mb: 4 }}>
          Vision & Mission
        </Typography>
        <Grid container spacing={4} sx={{ mb: 8 }}>
          {visionMission.map((item, index) => (
            <Grid item xs={12} md={6} key={index}>
              <VisionMissionCard {...item} />
            </Grid>
          ))}
        </Grid>

        {/* Achievements */}
        <Grid container spacing={4} sx={{ mb: 8 }}>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
            <StyledCard>
              <CardContent>
                <Box display="flex" alignItems="center" mb={2}>
                  <EmojiEvents sx={{ fontSize: 40, color: 'primary.main', mr: 2 }} />
                  <Typography variant="h5" color="primary">
                    Our Achievements
                  </Typography>
                </Box>
                <List>
                  {achievements.map((achievement, index) => (
                    <ListItem key={index}>
                      <ListItemIcon>
                        <CheckCircle color="primary" />
                      </ListItemIcon>
                      <ListItemText primary={achievement} />
                    </ListItem>
                  ))}
                </List>
              </CardContent>
            </StyledCard>
          </Grid>

          {/* Facilities */}
          <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
            <StyledCard>
              <CardContent>
                <Box display="flex" alignItems="center" mb={2}>
                  <School sx={{ fontSize: 40, color: 'primary.main', mr: 2 }} />
                  <Typography variant="h5" color="primary">
                    Our Facilities
                  </Typography>
                </Box>
                <List>
                  {facilities.map((facility, index) => (
                    <ListItem key={index}>
                      <ListItemIcon>
                        <CheckCircle color="primary" />
                      </ListItemIcon>
                      <ListItemText primary={facility} />
                    </ListItem>
                  ))}
                </List>
              </CardContent>
            </StyledCard>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>

        {/* Call to Action */}
        <Box textAlign="center">
          <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>
            Join Us at SECE
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
            Be part of our journey towards excellence in engineering education.
          </Typography>
          <Button
            variant="contained"
            color="primary"
            size="large"
            href="/admissions"
            sx={{ mt: 2 }}
          >
            Apply Now
          </Button>
        </Box>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default About;
